{"tid":974111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★微軟強推 Office 一月更新，大量辦公室 Excel 一開即崩潰","createTime":"2019-01-08T15:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"03c289d1db557cc510b8e0ec4698274a09ca4400","tid":974111,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"微軟不時推出更新，目的是修補漏洞及加入新功能等。在 1 月 2 日時，微軟向 Office 用戶推出了 1 月更新檔，而隨後這幾天已經陸續送到各用戶電腦上。不過，微軟每次的自動更新卻頻頻帶來問題，這一次更是嚴重到大量用戶的 Excel 程式崩潰，導打工仔今早想用 Excel 工作也不能。<br />\n<br />\n日前有用戶在微軟討論區上發貼表示 Excel 在更新後出現問題，隨即有 300 多名用戶表示遭遇到相同問題。而筆者今日亦收到大量朋友求助，紛紛表示無法開啟 Excel。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/screenshot_2686a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fscreenshot_2686a.jpg&h=58a1a422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/01/07/office-jan-2019-update-and-fix/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F01%2F07%2Foffice-jan-2019-update-and-fix%2F&d=RVE7oYzF4ieQY3de9c1%2B%2FsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e24bbac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/01/07/office-jan-2019-update-and-fix/</a>"},{"pid":"1852e7fb1aaa57e26af3b4857ab4c2330d0d7cbc","tid":974111,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02dc8c37d798635a5e7c4cfc0f2275d28d378c34","tid":974111,"uid":19454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"more FREE OT for HK slave<br />\n<br />\nMS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0e61239975739be74f960bc7df68793d436f5e","tid":9